         DoT stacking refers to multiple people casting the SAME DoT spell on the same creature and all of those DoTs working and not overwriting the last.</P><P><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=128276" target="_blank">Neriek Fizzlestab</a><BR><a href="http://pub21.ezboard.com/bhallofshadows" target="_blank">Delharen D'Oloth</a><BR><a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/board.asp?brd=5029" target="_blank">Veeshan</a></center><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
