         And even lowly me knew this long ago...  And I quote:<BR>08/06/2002 :  17:28:10             <BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>DoTs work the same as buffs. That's a huge problem. </P><P>If you can stack DOTs will that mean that you can stack regen? Because as I understand it they both use the same stacking/anti-stacking code. </P><P>The answer is a re-write of DOTs and Buffs and that's just not going to happen anytime soon.</P><P></P><P><center><BR>The 3yr old level 51 Necro...<img src=icon_smile_clown.gif border=0 align=middle><BR><img src="http://www.thisisnotacommunity.org/1.gif" border=0><img src="http://www.imahosting.com/sigs/legal.jpg" border=0></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
